name: An Enslaved Rebellion
description:
The Captain wailed at the crack of the whip on his own bare skin.
The Ship swayed and jerked across the windblown sea.
The Casa Maria had no idea this would be it's final voyage.
The Destination had now changed. The occupants were finally angry. Their blood had spilled for far too long. Their veins burst with rage.
All onboard when this vessel embarked would pay the price.
The Chosen ones had decided it was time to fight.
God had Blessed them all and they were indeed Holy and grateful.
